OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F468A1772899880
OL,3,CThree men with links to Wales bailed
OL,4,Cover alleged spying for China
OL,6,FThe husband of a Labour MP and two
OL,7,Fother men have been released on bail
OL,8,Fafter being arrested on suspicion of
OL,9,Fspying for China.
OL,11,FDavid Taylor, the husband of Scottish
OL,12,FLabour MP Joani Reid, is accused of
OL,13,Fassisting a foreign intelligence
OL,14,Fservice.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/7
