FL,469,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F468A1772899880
OL,3,CThree men with links to Wales bailed
OL,4,Cover alleged spying for China
OL,6,FTaylor, 39, alongside two other men,
OL,7,Faged 43 and 68, were arrested by
OL,8,Fcounter-terrorism officers at
OL,9,Faddresses in London and Wales on
OL,10,FWednesday and have been released on
OL,11,Fbail until May, the Metropolitan
OL,12,FPolice said.
OL,14,FFollowing Taylor's arrest, Ms Reid,
OL,15,Fwho sits on the Home Affairs Select
OL,16,FCommittee and is MP for East Kilbride
OL,17,Fand Strathaven, said she had "never
OL,18,Fseen anything to make me suspect my
OL,19,Fhusband has broken any law".
OL,26,@yD@^OU{D@[O]
