FL,469,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F468A1772899880
OL,3,CThree men with links to Wales bailed
OL,4,Cover alleged spying for China
OL,6,FThe three men were taken into custody
OL,7,Ffor questioning by police before being
OL,8,Freleased on bail.
OL,10,FThe policing operation came as
OL,11,Fsecurity minister Dan Jarvis told MPs
OL,12,FChinese officials in the UK and
OL,13,FBeijing had been given a dressing
OL,14,Fdown, and that the investigation
OL,15,Frelates to "foreign interference
OL,16,Ftargeting UK democracy".
OL,26,@wD@LOUxD@WO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/7
