FL,469,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F468A1772899880
OL,3,CThree men with links to Wales bailed
OL,4,Cover alleged spying for China
OL,6,FMet officers were seen at a property
OL,7,Flinked to one of the men in South
OL,8,FWales on Wednesday ` with a car
OL,9,Foutside the address being searched and
OL,10,Fphotographed.
OL,12,FTaylor, 39, is listed as a "lobbyist"
OL,13,Fon Ms Reid's registered interests.
OL,15,FCommander Helen Flanagan, head of
OL,16,FCounter Terrorism Policing London,
OL,17,Fpreviously said the force does not
OL,18,Fbelieve there to be "any imminent or
OL,19,Fdirect threat" related to the arrests.
OL,26,@tD@\OUtD@eO]zD@UOU{D@NO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/7
