OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,469,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F468A1772899880
OL,3,CThree men with links to Wales bailed
OL,4,Cover alleged spying for China
OL,6,FTaylor was arrested in London, the 43-
OL,7,Fyear-old man was arrested in
OL,8,FPontyclun, and the 68-year-old suspect
OL,9,Fwas arrested in Powys ` with all three
OL,10,Fbeing detained under the Police and
OL,11,FCriminal Evidence Act.
OL,13,FOther properties in London, East
OL,14,FKilbride in Scotland, and Cardiff have
OL,15,Falso been searched, the Met said.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G5/7
