FL,469,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F468A1772899880
OL,3,CThree men with links to Wales bailed
OL,4,Cover alleged spying for China
OL,6,FIn her statement after the arrests, Ms
OL,7,FReid ` the MP for East Kilbride and
OL,8,FStrathaven ` said: "I have never been
OL,9,Fto China. I have never spoken on China
OL,10,For China-related matters in the
OL,11,FCommons. I have never asked a question
OL,12,Fon China-related matters.
OL,14,F"As far as I am aware, I have never
OL,15,Fmet any Chinese businesses whilst I
OL,16,Fhave been an MP, any Chinese diplomats
OL,17,For government employees, nor raised
OL,18,Fany concern with ministers or anyone
OL,19,Felse on behalf of, even
OL,20,Fcoincidentally, Chinese interests."
OL,26,@pD@TOUvD@AOU|D@cO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G6/7
