OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,469,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F468A1772899880
OL,3,CThree men with links to Wales bailed
OL,4,Cover alleged spying for China
OL,6,FShe added: "I am not any sort of
OL,7,Fadmirer or apologist for the Chinese
OL,8,FCommunist Party's dictatorship.
OL,10,F"I have never seen anything to make me
OL,11,Fsuspect my husband has broken any law."
OL,26,@nD@LOUrD@AOUsD@gO]
